{"tid":879088,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★以為有工返好過冇工返，大錯特錯-----在職貧窮","createTime":"2018-10-27T15:58:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T05:49:32.000Z","uid":19454,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bff628b970906a900ff9ed6a1e957029c81437c8","tid":879088,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:58:31.000Z","msg":"如果你以為有工返，總好過冇工返，咁呢個諗法，就真係大錯特錯。須知道呢個世界上，有一樣嘢叫「在職貧窮」，既要返工做嘢辛苦，同時又要捱窮，相比起失業待業在家更慘。近有網民就大呻：「月入萬幾蚊嘅嗰班人，係全香港最慘嘅打工仔！」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>1. 在職貧窮：申請公屋唔夠資格</strong><br />\n根據現時公屋的基本申請資格，家庭人數一人入息及總資產淨值限額分別為$11,250及$245,000。<br />\n<br />\n如果你搵緊12K，Sorry！你已經超過申請一人家庭入息淨值限額上限喇！拜！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>2. 在職貧窮：私樓一世儲唔到錢買</strong><br />\n香港樓價有升無跌，今時今日所謂平價的上車盤，約200實呎的舊樓都過300萬。<br />\n<br />\n當搵緊3幾萬蚊人工嗰一群都大嗌上唔到車之時，試問一個搵萬零蚊嘅打工仔，又點可以買到私樓呢，簡直係天荒夜談啦！<br />\n<br />\n<strong>3. 在職貧窮：保險無錢供</strong><br />\n當每月份糧都唔夠個人基本生活費，每日返工嘅車費、飯錢，電話費都要計過度過先用嘅時候。<br />\n<br />\n莫講話再用額外錢嚟買保險，差啲就連睇醫生錢都未必畀得出！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>4. 在職貧窮：<span style=\"color: red;\">搵唔到女朋友</span></strong><br />\n雖則話拍拖最緊要係「兩情相悅」，之但係唔係有情就真係可以飲水飽嘅。<br />\n<br />\n當自己都差啲淨係得水飲嘅時間，就無謂累其他人要陪你飲水啦，嗚！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 在職貧窮：父母嫌家用少<br />\n仔女有收入，畀家用父母係天經地義嘅事，但係搵得雞碎咁多，又真係好難畀得多父母。<br />\n<br />\n與此同時，父母嫌家用唔夠亦都係人之常情，始終燈油火蠟樣樣都要錢，兩難呀唉！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%BE%E8%9A%8A-%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%B7%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE-%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%85%E6%A5%AD%E6%9B%B4%E6%85%98-104103402.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BB%2594%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A5%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%25B9%25BE%25E8%259A%258A-%25E5%259C%25A8%25E8%2581%25B7%25E8%25B2%25A7%25E7%25AA%25AE-%25E7%259B%25B8%25E6%25AF%2594%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E5%25BE%2585%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E6%259B%25B4%25E6%2585%2598-104103402.html&d=OrZzllHdXYNnOBfAsZKE9GMi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=9792df47\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/news/%E6%89%93%E5%B7%A5%E4%BB%94%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A5%E8%90%AC%E5%B9%BE%E8%9A%8A-%E5%9C%A8%E8%81%B7%E8%B2%A7%E7%AA%AE-%E7%9B%B8%E6%AF%94%E5%A4%B1%E6%A5%AD%E5%BE%85%E6%A5%AD%E6%9B%B4%E6%85%98-104103402.html</a>"},{"pid":"a27a2b117030a5cd3afc5ff092786e70183bfd3f","tid":879088,"uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T15:59:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F133811_1d9fcb4f63a440a77c32deb42756910e.png&h=529146e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d1e2ca6f79f1801306f5d660fa26da2e8d97878c","tid":879088,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:01:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/145435_08be2aa0dd2179c6a2f5111a18d912fc.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F145435_08be2aa0dd2179c6a2f5111a18d912fc.gif&h=b0391598&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"217d0308c088053ebc9fac357dedc7bc6049db60","tid":879088,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:01:47.000Z","msg":"廢老：覺得人工少，點解唔夜晚返多份pt?"},{"pid":"2062db377f8f9590c756ba35491ee0585837499b","tid":879088,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:02:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/29/133214_aa45756cb29a102940c70b765c4f7598.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F29%2F133214_aa45756cb29a102940c70b765c4f7598.gif&h=dcc02f8c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3db59d06ab794fec53783968b1b495fb9a9a1e46","tid":879088,"uid":119502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T16:02:06.000Z","msg":"可唔可以教下點攞綜緩?"},{"pid":"f99502bdb59663eb6834ae4c691b